OL,3,CPoll finds majority support assisted
OL,4,Cdying law change in Jersey
OL,6,FShe added: "This historic debate is a
OL,7,Fcritical opportunity for States
OL,8,FMembers to do the right thing and pave
OL,9,Fthe way for a safer, kinder, more
OL,10,Fcompassionate law for dying people."
OL,12,FHowever, the issue has sparked heated
OL,13,Fdebate on both sides, with protestors
OL,14,Fexpected to gather outside the States
OL,15,FAssembly ahead of the debate on
OL,16,FTuesday 21 May.
OL,18,FThose in support of legalisation have
OL,19,Fhanded an open letter with more than
OL,20,F3,100 signatures to Chief Minister
OL,21,FLyndon Farnham.
